00:25:35,561 --> 00:25:37,804
_

263
00:25:38,084 --> 00:25:40,472
_

264
00:25:44,925 --> 00:25:46,564
You saw something out there?

265
00:25:46,625 --> 00:25:49,817
The Orc I pursued out of
Lake-town, I know who he is.

266
00:25:49,856 --> 00:25:53,269
Bolg, the spawn of
Azog the Defiler.

267
00:25:53,329 --> 00:25:56,499
A Wargpack was waiting for him
on the outskirts of Esgorath.

268
00:25:56,528 --> 00:25:58,309
They fled into the north.

269
00:25:58,329 --> 00:26:00,001
These Orcs were different
from the others,

270
00:26:00,021 --> 00:26:02,891
they bore a mark I had not
seen for a long time.

271
00:26:02,911 --> 00:26:04,711
The mark of Gundabad.

272
00:26:04,731 --> 00:26:06,042
Gundabad?

273
00:26:06,073 --> 00:26:09,472
An Orc stronghold in the far
north of the Misty Mountains.

274
