00:29:24,161 --> 00:29:26,088
I am not alone.

300
00:29:38,005 --> 00:29:40,523
Are you in need of
assistance, My Lady?

301
00:29:45,077 --> 00:29:46,898
You should have stayed...

302
00:29:46,969 --> 00:29:48,467
dead!

303
00:30:14,567 --> 00:30:16,108
Mithrandir...

304
00:30:18,211 --> 00:30:20,750
come back.

305
00:30:35,424 --> 00:30:37,896
H- He is here.

306
00:30:37,926 --> 00:30:42,760
He is. The darkness
has returned.

307
00:30:50,144 --> 00:30:52,201
Gandalf!

308
00:30:54,013 --> 00:30:54,953
Gandalf,

309
00:30:55,003 --> 00:30:56,105
climb on!

310
00:30:56,134 --> 00:30:58,237
He is weak.

311
00:30:58,267 --> 00:31:02,186
He cannot remain here, it
is straining his life.

312
00:31:02,217 --> 00:31:03,438
Go,

313
00:31:03,468 --> 00:31:04,469
quickly!

314
00:31:06,307 --> 00:31:08,749
Come with me, My...

315
00:31:08,778 --> 00:31:11,040
Lady.

316
00:31:18,192 --> 00:31:19,233
Go!

