00:32:24,517 --> 00:32:27,098
You have no...

323
00:32:27,138 --> 00:32:29,590
power here,

324
00:32:29,621 --> 00:32:32,630
servant of Mordor.

325
00:32:34,121 --> 00:32:35,142
You...

326
00:32:35,182 --> 00:32:38,674
are nameless,

327
00:32:40,212 --> 00:32:42,855
faceless,

328
00:32:42,894 --> 00:32:46,177
formless!

329
00:32:49,106 --> 00:32:52,829
Go back to the void...

330
00:32:52,849 --> 00:32:58,480
from whence you came!

